  "description": {
    "zh": "嗨，战士。过来，我有一个任务安排给你。你应该也知道，我对外出售一些高价值的设备和货物，也会派狗腿们在塔科夫到处寻找战利品。现在的情况是，订单量巨他妈的多，但是不加准备就让小弟们跑长途又很危险。现在是你出来救场的时候了。简单来说，你得提供一条安全的通道，让那些原来的PMC们不会打我小弟们的主意。看着，我给你指一下路线。记清楚了吗？很好。要求是你得一次性全部完成，我的小弟们可不会等着你。所以，加油，战士，不要让我失望。",
    "en": "Hello there, warrior. C'mere, I've got a task for you. As you know, I sell various equipment and supplies, and send my people to search for loot throughout whole Tarkov. The thing is, I've got a shit ton of orders right now, and sending my guys into a long raid without proper protection is too dangerous. That's where you come to the rescue. In short, you have to provide a safe passage for them throughout the route, press the local ex-PMCs to not think of attacking the guys. Here, let me show you the route on the map. Memorized it? Good. The catch is that all this needs to be done in one go, my guys will not wait if something happens to you. So come on, warrior, don't let me down."
  },
